## 3. Enable GitHub Pages

1. In your repo go to **Settings** → scroll down to **Pages**
2. Under **Source** select **Deploy from a branch**
3. Under **Branch** select **main** → **/ (root)**
4. Click **Save**
5. Wait 2-3 minutes

Your URLs will be:
- `https://nathantang.github.io/pokerlog-privacy`
- `https://nathantang.github.io/pokerlog-privacy/terms`
- `https://nathantang.github.io/pokerlog-privacy/disclaimer`

